author: Jorge Alonso
title: Kirk Cousins Throws Interception Then Chases Down Aqib Talib And Strips Ball Away
text:
Say what you want to say about Kirk Cousins but the dude has heart.
After throwing an interception in the meaningless Pro Bowl, Kirk Cousins never quit on the play and ending up chasing down Broncos corner Aqib Talib. 
Although Cousins was able to strip the ball away,the AFC still ended up recovery the ball.
